examples.en: The cliff was shrouded in mist.
Joseph was shrouded under a dark blanket.
The work is shrouded in secrecy.
The mountains were shrouded in fog.
Their work is shrouded in secrecy.
The incident has always been shrouded in mystery.
examples.ru: Это происшествие всегда было окутано тайной.

examples.en: The project has been shrouded in controversy from its inception.
examples.ru: С самого начала вокруг данного проекта ведутся бурные споры.

examples.en: Next morning, the whole town was shrouded in mist (=covered in mist).
examples.ru: На следующее утро весь город был окутан (т.е. покрыт) туманом.
